#: ''Hätten Sie wohl '''mal''' Feuer?'' (“''Do you have a [[lighter]], [please]?''”) — May be considered appropriate towards a stranger; politeness is reinforced by the subjunctive ({{m|de|hätten}}) and the additional adverb {{m|de|wohl}}.
